Final
Objective: create and format a word processing report
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bZQX3XwAayQ 
Intro: This video will show you how to do the things I want you to prove to end this unit.
Copy Paste one of your “Month in Review” essays into word.
Change the margins to 2 inches 
Create a header just like this guy did in the video but with “Professor H, your class period, and your name instead of “Report 2”
Title your essay and place in the middle
Set your spacing to double space @2:43 in video
Somewhere in this essay change the color of the text to blue, purple or red.
Add one image with the text formatted AROUND the image
Add one arrow pointing to something (a picture or more text…)
